Sit Fixed Income Portfolio Management
The firm’s 18 fixed income investment professionals have over 336 years of combined investment management experience.  The average number of years of experience is 18.7.    Our fixed income investment expertise is in both taxable and municipal strategies and emphasize a high level of interest income and stability of principal using investment-grade securities.  We also have expertise in alternative fixed-income strategies.


