Executive Profile
Roger J. Sit  Chairman, Chief Executive Officer, President and Global Chief Investment Officer, Sit Investment Associates, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 14 different industries.See Board Relationships55--
Background

		Mr. Roger J. Sit serves as the Chairman, Chief Executive Officer, Co-President and Global Chief Investment Officer at Sit Investment Associates, Inc., where Mr. Sit joined in January 1998 and directs investment management activities. He serves as a Portfolio Manager of Sit Mutual Funds in its fund complex. He was an Equity Analyst of Goldman Sachs Group Inc., Research Division. Mr. Sit served as a Vice President and Senior Equity Research Analyst at Goldman Sachs & Co. ... in New York for seven years. He was a Captain in the U.S. Air Force and served for six years in active duty with financial management responsibilities at Headquarters Space Division. He serves as Chairman of Sit Money Market Fund Inc. He has been a Director of TCF Financial Corporation since January 22, 2015. He serves on the Boards of Convergent Capital, the Minneapolis Institute of Arts and the Minneapolis Club. He graduated with Military Distinction from the U.S. Air Force Academy in 1984. He has a M.S. in Systems Technology from the University of Southern California in 1987 and an M.B.A. with honors from the Harvard Graduate School of Business in 1991.Read Full Background




